<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.9.2">
<l>tiṇṇiyatō rariyuruvāyt ticaiyaṉaittum naṭuṅkat tēvaroṭu tāṉavarkaḷ ticaippavira ṇiyaṉai</l>
<l>naṇṇiyavaṉ mārvakalat tukirmaṭutta nātaṉ nāṭōṟum makiḻntiṉitu maruviyuṟai kōyil</l>
<l>eṇṇilmiku peruñcelvat teḻilviḷaṅku maṟaiyu mēḻicaiyuṅ kēḷvikaḷu miyaṉṟaperuṅ kuṇattōr</l>
<l>maṇṇilmiku maṟaiyavarkaḷ maliveytu nāṅkūr vaikunta viṇṇakaram vaṇaṅkumaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Simple heart, worship in Vaikunta Viṇṇakaram in Nānkūr which acquires</l>
<l rend="indent">	the best of Vedic experts on earth,</l>
<l>Those of great qualities suited to scholarship, the seven melodies,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the Vedas, whose beauty of superior, great,</l>
<l rend="indent">immeasurable learning shines,</l>
<l>The temple where dwells the lord, happily with affection [and] rejoicing daily,</l>
<l rend="indent">who, in the form of a brawny lion having clasped Hiraṇya,</l>
<l>Sunk his claws into his broad chest so that the cardinal points shook</l>
<l rend="indent">and the deva-s and dānava-s were amazed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
